  "name": "Nagaraja COU1 — Non-cannulated pedicle screw compression-bending credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for FEA prediction of ASTM F1717 static compression-bending performance of a non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw construct. The FEA model ensemble (FDA, Ansys, DePuy Synthes) is compared against N=11 experimental constructs across two independent laboratories. All 13 V&V 40 credibility factors have been assessed; the Test Conditions factor falls one gradation below the required level owing to a single test condition being evaluated. The intended use scope — prediction of construct stiffness and failure load under quasi-static compression-bending for a Class II spinal fixation device — is described in the Claim and Requirement nodes bound to this assurance unit.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/req/f1717-compression-bending-fea-prediction",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/claim/fea-predicts-f1717-static-performance",
  "bindsModel": "https://uofa.net/nagaraja/model/pedicle-screw-fea-ensemble-v2",
